lead_paragraph: With Drew Brees' big arm, a 1-2 running punch in Mark Ingram and Tim Hightower and all of those capable receiving targets, the New Orleans Saints suddenly are looking like a legitimate contender again.

headline.print_headline: Brees Leads Saints to Fourth Win in Five After 0-3 Start
